script.name: !move.resupply.self
script.sourceplaintext:
skip if $a.ware return FLRET_NOCOMMANDS skip if $a.qty > 0 return FLRET_NOCOMMANDS skip if [THIS] -> can transport ware $a.ware return FLRET_NOCOMMANDS $this.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $a.ware in cargo bay skip if $this.free >= $a.qty return FLRET_NOCARGO
$cmd.extra = [THIS] ->get command extra display override
$average.price = get average price of ware $a.ware $IS.PLAYER = [TRUEOWNER] == Player if [THIS] -> is autojump activated if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Navigation Command Software MK1 in cargo bay if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $energy.got = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $energy.needed = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy: jumps=1 $jump.range = $energy.got / $energy.needed end end end end
skip if $jump.range > 0 $jump.range = 0
$MAX.JUMPS = $a.maxFly + $jump.range skip if $MAX.JUMPS < 20 $MAX.JUMPS = 20 $exclude.table.docked = table alloc $exclude.table.this = table alloc $blacklist.sectors = table alloc $safe.sectors = table alloc
gosub sub.GetDockedShip $try.resupply.ship = $docked.ship
while [TRUE] @ = wait 100 ms
do if is a new script version available return FLRET_NOCARGO
* fly to ware and buy * find local supply if $station -> exists gosub sub.CheckStation if $station $station.owner = $station -> get owner race if [OWNER] == $station.owner $amt = $station -> get amount of ware $a.ware in cargo bay else $amt = $station -> get true amount of ware $a.ware in cargo bay end skip if $amt >= $a.qty $station = null end end
if not $station if $IS.PLAYER gosub sub.CheckThis $player.range = 1 gosub sub.FindPlayer
if not $station gosub sub.CheckDocked gosub sub.FindPlayer end end
$ret.blocked.station = [FALSE] if not $station gosub sub.CheckThis gosub sub.FindLocal end
if not $station gosub sub.CheckDocked gosub sub.FindLocal end
do if $ret.blocked.station AND ! $station continue
* or look for best buy if we need to travel any distance if not $station gosub sub.FindFurtherAll
do if $ret.blocked.station AND ! $station continue end end
*do if [THIS] -> is in active sector *write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='%s: Found station = %s', [THIS], $station, $station, null, null
* if we get there, then theres no other possibilities if not $station [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$cmd.extra return FLRET_CANTDOCK end if not is datatype[ $station ] == DATATYPE_STATION [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$cmd.extra return FLRET_CANTDOCK end
* station is destroyed? if not $station -> exists @ = wait 100 ms $station = null continue end
$this.cmd = [THIS] -> get command
if $this.cmd != COMMAND_NONE $text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2152, $station, null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text end
* If we found a station to buy at if [THIS] ->can fly through gates $station.sector = $station -> get sector if not $station.sector -> exists @ = wait 100 ms $station = null continue end
if $station.sector != [SECTOR] @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector : sector=$station.sector if $ret == FLRET_NOPATH $blacklist.sectors[$station.sector] = [TRUE] @ = wait 100 ms continue end end end
@ = wait 1000 ms gosub sub.GetRange
$this.speed = [THIS] -> get current max speed
if $trader == [TRUEOWNER] $trader.speed = get ship max speed from shiptype: Freight Drone $trader.speed = $trader.speed / [Units.M] if [THIS] -> is in same sector as $station if $this.speed > $trader.speed @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoobject : Target=$station Range=$range end end
$drone = [THIS] ->eject ware: ware=Freight Drone if $drone -> exists $trader = $drone else @ = wait 100 ms continue end end
if $trader != [THIS] if $station -> exists $trader.speed = [THIS] -> get current max speed
do if [THIS] -> is docked @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.undock :
if [THIS] -> is in same sector as $station $dist = get distance between [THIS] and $station if $trader -> is docked if $this.speed > $trader.speed AND ( $dist + 1000 ) > $range @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoobject : Target=$station Range=$range end end end
$wares.table = table alloc $wares.table[$a.ware] = $a.qty $old.homebase = $trader -> get homebase $trader ->set homebase to [THIS] $old.amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $a.ware in cargo bay $trader ->set is being managed: on=[TRUE] @ START $trader -> call script !ship.cmd.freightfetch.std : Target=$station Ware Table=$wares.table Return Home=[TRUE]
if [THIS] -> is in same sector as $station $dist = get distance between [THIS] and $station gosub sub.GetRange if $dist > $range @ = [THIS] ->fly to object $station: timeout=2000 ms else @ = wait 2000 ms end else @ = wait 2000 ms end
while $trader -> is script !ship.cmd.freightfetch.std on stack of task=0 @ = wait 100 ms if not [THIS] -> is in same sector as $station @ = wait 2000 ms else $dist = get distance between [THIS] and $station gosub sub.GetRange if $dist > $range @ = [THIS] ->fly to object $station: timeout=2000 ms else @ = wait 2000 ms end end
skip if $trader -> exists break end
if $trader -> exists $trader ->set homebase to $old.homebase $trader ->set is being managed: on=[FALSE] else gosub sub.GetDockedShip $try.resupply.ship = $docked.ship end
$current.amt = [THIS] -> get amount of ware $a.ware in cargo bay $bought.quantity = $current.amt - $old.amt end else $arrived = null if $station -> exists [THIS] ->set destination to $station @ $bought.quantity = [THIS] -> call script !trade.getware : ware=$a.ware destination station=$station amount=$a.qty min price=null end end
$a.qty = $a.qty - $bought.quantity skip if $a.qty > 0 break @ = wait 1000 ms end
[THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$cmd.extra return FLRET_OK
sub.GetRange: if [THIS] -> is in active sector $size.this = [THIS] -> get size of object $size.station = [THIS] -> get size of object $range = $size.station + $size.this + 5000 else $range = 2000 end endsub
sub.CheckThis: $trader = [THIS] $exclude.table = $exclude.table.this endsub
sub.CheckDocked: $trader = $try.resupply.ship $exclude.table = $exclude.table.docked endsub
sub.GetDockedShip: * if we have freight drones, priorities those if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Freight Drone in cargo bay $docked.ship = [TRUEOWNER] endsub end
if [THIS] -> is of class Carrier @ = wait 100 ms $best.ship = null $best.free = 0 $docked.ships = [THIS] -> get ship array from sector/ship/station $docked.ship.i = size of array $docked.ships while $docked.ship.i dec $docked.ship.i = $docked.ship = $docked.ships[$docked.ship.i]
$docked.owner = $docked.ship -> get true owner skip if [TRUEOWNER] == $docked.owner continue
skip if $docked.ship -> can transport ware $a.ware continue
$ship.cmd = $docked.ship -> get command do if $ship.cmd AND $ship.cmd != COMMAND_NONE continue
$docked.free = $docked.ship -> get free amount of ware $a.ware in cargo bay skip if $docked.free continue
if $a.qty > $docked.free if $docked.free > $best.free $best.ship = $docked.ship $best.free = $docked.free end else if $best.ship $speed = $docked.ship -> get current max speed $best.speed = $best.ship -> get current max speed do if $speed > $best.speed $best.ship = $docked.ship else $best.free = $a.qty $best.ship = $docked.ship end end $docked.ship = $best.ship end endsub
sub.FindPlayer: if $IS.PLAYER if $trader $table.player = table alloc $player.stations = get ship array: of race [TRUEOWNER] class/type=Dock if $player.stations $i = size of array $player.stations while $i @ = wait 1 ms dec $i = $station = $player.stations[$i] $amt = $station -> get amount of ware $a.ware in cargo bay skip if $amt >= $a.qty continue
$p.sector = $station -> get sector $jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $p.sector if $jumps <= $MAX.JUMPS gosub sub.CheckStation if $station $table.player[$station] = $jumps end end end end
if size of table $table.player $sorted.array = sort table keys by value: table=$table.player $station = get first item in array: $sorted.array else $station = null end end end
endsub
sub.FindLocal: if $trader $station = find station: product $a.ware with min. jumps: max.price=$average.price, amount=$a.qty, max.jumps=0, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=$trader, exclude array=$exclude.table gosub sub.CheckStation
if not $station $station = find station sells: resource $a.ware with min. jumps: max.price=null, amount=null, max.jumps=0, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=$trader, exclude array=$exclude.table gosub sub.CheckStation end
if not $station $station = find station: product $a.ware with min. jumps: max.price=null, amount=$a.qty, max.jumps=1, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=$trader, exclude array=$exclude.table gosub sub.CheckStation end end endsub
sub.FindFurtherAll: if not $station gosub sub.CheckThis $player.range = $MAX.JUMPS gosub sub.FindPlayer if not $station gosub sub.CheckDocked gosub sub.FindFurther end
$ret.blocked.station = [FALSE] if not $station gosub sub.CheckThis gosub sub.FindFurther end
if not $station gosub sub.CheckDocked gosub sub.FindFurther end end endsub
sub.FindFurther: if $trader if not $station $station = find station: product $a.ware with best price depend on jumps: max.price=null, amount=null, max.jumps=$MAX.JUMPS, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=$trader, exclude array=$exclude.table gosub sub.CheckStation end
if not $station $station = find station sells: resource $a.ware with best price depend on jumps: max.price=null, amount=null, max.jumps=$MAX.JUMPS, startsector=[SECTOR], trader=$trader, exclude array=$exclude.table gosub sub.CheckStation end end endsub
* check for a valid destination sub.CheckStation: if $station -> exists if $trader -> exists if $trader == [TRUEOWNER] $docking.allowed = $trader -> is docking allowed at $station $docking.possible = [TRUE] else $docking.allowed = $trader -> is docking allowed at $station $docking.possible = $station -> is docking possible of $trader end else $docking.possible = null $docking.allowed = null end
$station.owner = $station -> get owner race if $station.owner == Player AND [TRUEOWNER] != Player if $station -> only player own ships can trade with $docking.possible = [FALSE] $docking.allowed = [FALSE] end end
if ! $docking.allowed OR ! $docking.allowed $exclude.table[$station] = $station $station = null else $station.sector = $station -> get sector if $blacklist.sectors[$station.sector] $exclude.table[$station] = $station $station = null else if not $safe.sectors[$station.sector] if is valid route between sectors [SECTOR] and $station.sector $safe.sectors[$station.sector] = [TRUE] if $IS.PLAYER if [THIS] ->can fly through gates @ if not [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$station Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[FALSE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=null $blacklist.sectors[$station.sector] = [TRUE] remove key $station.sector from table $safe.sectors $exclude.table[$station] = $station $station = null end @ = wait 10 ms end end else $blacklist.sectors[$station.sector] = [TRUE] end end end if $exclude.table[$station] $station = null end
skip if $station $ret.blocked.station = [TRUE] end endsub return null
